# SCENARIO PREMISE
#   T+48 hours after the Albion Battery Hall incident.
#   Players are the Meridian Claims Team. Albion Energy Storage has filed
#   an £8.2M claim. Task: verify the forensic causal chain, assess warranty
#   compliance, and make a coverage recommendation.
#
#   Recommended predecessor: Case 2 — "Albion Battery Hall: Code Red"
