# IMPLEMENTATION STATUS
# ==========================================================================
#
# IMPLEMENTED — no additional work required
#   Pin locks (archive door, underwriting cabinet)
#   Readable note objects (all document props)
#   Phone NPC system (Whitworth, Osei, Ngata) — full Ink dialogue trees compiled
#   Eleanor Vance person NPC — full Ink dialogue tree compiled
#   Forensic Data Platform terminal (MG-02) — self-contained client-side minigame,
#     no Hacktivity VM required
#   Claims Management System terminal (MG-01)
#   Warranty Compliance Checklist (MG-04)
#   Coverage Decision Form (MG-05)
#   eventMappings (all state transitions)
#
# PLACEHOLDER SPRITES — functional copies; replace with custom assets before release
#   coverage_decision_form.png  → copied from notes3.png
#   checklist.png               → copied from notes4.png
#   Eleanor Vance character     → using female_office_worker sprite (needs inspector_female variant)
